        (1700258, 'Kokowh', 2011, 1844, 6, 154, 5650000, 43000000, 'Henry is a playboy who has no idea that he is the father of a beautiful, cute girl out of a One-night-Stand. Her mother left the daughter in front of Henry door after her husband realized after 8 years of marriage that he is not the father so their relationship now is breaking up... By the way: Kokowh, is how a German (in this case an 8 Year old child) that has never heard the dish before - would pronounce "Coq Au Vin" (chicken in a wine sauce).', '/sjHbidT3IP6mR3ryNgrQ2ePxtmV.jpg', '/tXcWlYPgJsw9xN8wUoYfprW19sC.jpg', 0),
